You can have a total of 24 stored patches according to the owner’s manual. Comes with built-in tuner. The amp is rated at 5 watts. This is also a great travel guitar. Comes with soft case, AC adapter and Owner’s Manual. You can view all the specs and the manual at http://www.fernandesguitars.com/support/downloads/cat_view/69-nomad-deluxe.html Make sure you select the “Zoom – 2000 Version”.
